activities: FrontEnd Holdings LLC is a 3PL Storage and Fulfillment Warehouse. We do warehousing for the Movie Studio Industry. Currently we warehouse Props, Sets, Wardrobe Items, and Promotional material for a variety of Studios. We have the opportunity to get additional Storage business from a variety of studios by warehousing contracts and leagal documents related to the making of movies and these Studios are requiring us to be Safe Harbor Certified in order for us to bid on this business. We do not own any of the inventory we store nor do we access it. We simply store wrapped pallets and make pallets accessable to our customers upon request.
